Deola Sagoe recently unveiled her collection Komole: Nigeria’s Regal Gift To The World. The advertorial features four models from different races. Despite the  Yoruba song playing in the background, this ad has come under serious critisicim as Nigerians have alleged it pays little or no attention to the Nigerian women who patronize her. Some have said that no white woman would want to be seen tying the gele unless it is a Nigerian wedding. See the ad causing the outrage:  Read Nigerians reactions below:      On the other hand, some have said that they do not see anything wrong with the advert:     